{"word":"G5467 - χαλεπός - chalepós - khal-ep-os' - Fierce","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χαλεπός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">chalepós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">khal-ep-os'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Fierce</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"கொடிய - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"hard"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Perhaps from <a href=\"#/G5465 - χαλάω - chaláō - khal-ah'-o/5465\">G5465</a> through the idea of <i>reducing</i> the strength; <i>difficult</i>, that is, <i>dangerous</i>, or (by implication) <i>furious:</i> - fierce, perilous.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}